mixin readMore(shortText, longText)
	//- We have a circular reference using attributes "id", "for", _and_
	//- "aria-labelledby" to satisfy accessibility guidelines when using
	//- role="button". Otherwise audits will complain that the button
	//- has no text, even though it has a label.
	- const id = `readmore__checkbox-${COUNTER++}`;
	- const labelId = `readmore__label-${COUNTER++}`;

	input.readmore__checkbox(id=id type="checkbox" role="button" aria-labelledby=labelId)
	.readmore__short!= shortText
	.readmore__long!= longText
	label.readmore__label(id=labelId for=id) Read moreâ€¦
